enum.name: CATArrangementRouteSection
enum.abstract: Section Types for ArrangementRun, ArrangementPathway and ArrangementBoundary objects.

enum.name: CATArrangementRouteVisuMode
enum.abstract: The visualization mode for the ArrangementRun, ArrangementPathway, ArrangementBoundary objects.

method.name: GenerateBOMReport
method.abstract: This method generate a BOM report on the current piping document to an output html file.

class.name: ArrBendableString
class.abstract:
The interface to access a CATIAArrBendableString

Using this prefered syntax will enable mkdoc to document your class.

method.name: GetNumOfSegments
method.abstract: Returns the cumulative number of the straight/arc segments that make up the Bendable object.

method.name: GetNumOfSegmentsLocalAxis
method.abstract: Returns the cumulative number of the straight/arc segments that make up the Bendable object.

method.name: GetSegmentData
method.abstract: Returns the data of the segment (Point Indices, Slope angle, Rotation Angle).

method.name: InstanceName
method.abstract: Returns the Bendable's Instance Name.

class.name: ArrNomenclature
class.abstract: Represents the UserNomenclature object.

method.name: IsSystemNomenclature
method.abstract: Returns TRUE if the nomenclature happens to be a system nomenclature.

method.name: IconName
method.abstract: Gets/Sets the Icon Name associated to the Type Name.

method.name: IntSysClassName
method.abstract: Gets/Sets the internal class names for System nomenclatures.

method.name: SubTypes
method.abstract: Returns the collection of subtype UserNomenclatures within this UserNomenclature.

class.name: ArrNomenclatureTree
class.abstract: Represents the root User Dictionary object.

method.name: GetNomenclature
method.abstract: Finds a UserNomenclature by Name from this UserDictionary.

method.name: BaseNomenclatures
method.abstract: Returns the collection of BaseNomenclatures within this UserDictionary.

class.name: ArrNomenclatures
class.abstract: The collection of UserNomenclature objects.

method.name: AddUserNomenclature
method.abstract: Creates a new UserNomenclature and adds it to this collection.

class.name: ArrSystemLineProduct
class.abstract:
The interface to access a CATIAArrSystemLineProduct

Using this prefered syntax will enable mkdoc to document your class.

method.name: GetSubItem
method.abstract: Allows the user to get the item at a specific index location.

method.name: GetSubProductsCount
method.abstract: Returns the count of the sub-products that make up the System-Line Arrangement Product and that match a specifc interface id.

class.name: ArrWorkbench
class.abstract: Returns the Arrangement Workbench.

method.name: AddNomenclatureTree
method.abstract: This method allows the user to add a nomenclature tree if the get_ArrNomenclatureTree returns a Return code of E_FAIL.

method.name: ConvertArrangementProductToProduct
method.abstract: This method converts an ArrangementProduct back to a Product.

method.name: ConvertProductToArrangementProduct
method.abstract: This method converts a Product to an ArrangementProduct.

method.name: FindInterface
method.abstract: This method returns a interface handle as specified by the input interface name and the input interface handle.

method.name: ArrNomenclatureTree
method.abstract: Returns the ArrNomenclatureTree.

class.name: ArrangementArea
class.abstract: Use this object to access an ArrangementArea object's properties and functions.

method.name: GetTechnologicalObject
method.abstract: Returns the applicative data whose type is the given parameter.

method.name: ArrangementContours
method.abstract: Returns the ArrangementContours collection object associated with an ArrangementArea object.

method.name: Height
method.abstract: Returns or sets the Height of an ArrangementArea object.

method.name: Size
method.abstract: Returns the Size of the ArrangementArea.

method.name: VisuMode
method.abstract: Returns or sets the Visualization Mode for an ArrangementArea object.

class.name: ArrangementAreas
class.abstract: A Collection object for ArrangementArea objects.

method.name: AddArea
method.abstract: Creates a ArrangementArea and adds it to the collection.

method.name: Item
method.abstract: Returns the specified item of the collection.

method.name: Remove
method.abstract: Removes the specified ArrangementArea object from the collection.
